'''Brett''' is a bartender at the hotel where Meredith's hearing was taking place.

==History==
Brett served Maggie drinks at the bar while everyone else was at the hearing. Maggie took his pen and drew a picture on a napkin to explain Sabrina's problem to Brett. She asked him if he had a red pen, but he said he didn't and actually needed the other pen back.

==Career==
He is a bartender at a hotel.
